parameters:
Commander: Combat training begins now!! Everyone, take your
positions!!

Rough Soldier: Today's training partner is, heh, my lucky
day

Rough Soldier: Training with monsters ain't bad, but if you
can beat this one, you get to "use her as you like".

Menacing Mercenary: She might be shackled and slow, but
she's especially strong among our sparring partners. I'll
have to put some real effort into this.

Menacing Mercenary: Well, more importantly, it's not often
you get the chance to beat the crap out of such a fine
woman. In that sense, I'm gonna enjoy this... Hehehe.

Rough Soldier: It'd be a waste for the newbie to "pass out
during the fight and wake up after everything's over". How
about we team up and take down this combat doll...!

Commander: Everyone, don't break formation. Let's begin.
Charge!!!

Commander: With that, today's combat training is concluded!
From this moment on, you are free to do as you please!
Prepare yourselves so that you can perform without fail in
the next training! Dismissed!!
Commander: That's too much! You damn combat doll!!

Commander: With that, today's combat training is concluded!
From this moment on, you are free to do as you please!
Prepare yourselves so that you can perform without fail in
the next training! Dismissed!!
